<item>
            <title>[LU-9396] kms_shift_cb ldlm debug is too expensive</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9396</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The LDLM_DEBUG debug statement in kms_shift_cb is too expensive, and under real workloads with +dlmtrace, it tends to lead to RCU stalls.  Under certain loads, this debug can be called for most/all of the locks on a resource while the resource spin lock is held.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is just too expensive, and the debug doesn&apos;t add that much.  Remove it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
